results.story: The 2024 edition of the Air Jordan 4 Retro TD ‘Military Blue’ brings back an OG colorway in time for the classic silhouette’s 35th anniversary. True to the original, the upper features off-white leather construction with quarter panel netting and TPU support wings. Military Blue lands on the upper and lower eyelets, along with a heel tab marked with Nike Air branding. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a two-tone foam midsole, reinforced underfoot by a herringbone-traction outsole.
